setAdvertisementSettings(int, int, int, int, int, int, int) - Method in class com.ssia.sticknfind.sdk.LeSnfDevice
Set/change Advertisement Settings Timings are in 1.25ms steps For no active connection advertise with following settings: (1) fast for timeout_fast (2) middle till timeout_slow is reached (3) continue with slow For channel_txpower params: lowest 4 bits -> 0:-40dBm 1:-20dBm 2:-16dBm 3:-12dBm 4:-8dBm 5:-4dBm 6: 0dBm 7:+4dBm next 4 bits -> enables channels: 0x10:ch37 0x20:ch38 0x40:ch39 example: 0x76 -> ch37-39 are sending with 0dBm channel + power: high 4 bits: enabled channels(ch37: 0x10, ch38:0x20, ch39:0x40, low 4 bits: tx-power (0: -40dBm,-20dBm,-16dBm,-12dBm,-8dBm,-4dBm,0dBm, 7: 4dBm)
